title: Line drilling machine US-MZ73212
short_description: This US-MZ73212 model wood drill has a power of 1.5KW*2 and also works at an air pressure of 0.6-0.8 MPa. The maximum cutting diameter of the equipment is 35 mm and the maximum cutting depth is 60 mm. The overall dimensions of the equipment are 2000 x 2500 x 1600 mm.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-MZ73212 modeldagi yog'och burg'ulash uskunasi  1.5KW*2 quvvatga ega, shuningdek, 0.6-0.8 mpa havo bosimida ishlaydi. Uskunaning maksimal kesish diametri 35 mm hamda maksimal kesish chuqurligi esa 60 mmni tashkil etadi. Uskunaning umumiy o'lchamlari esa 2000 x 2500 x 1600 mmni tashkil etadi.
short_description_ru: Эта дрель по дереву модели US-MZ73212 имеет мощность 1,5 кВт*2 и работает при давлении воздуха 0,6-0,8 МПа. Максимальный диаметр реза оборудования составляет 35 мм, а максимальная глубина реза — 60 мм. Габаритные размеры оборудования 2000 х 2500 х 1600 мм.
short_description_en: This US-MZ73212 model wood drill has a power of 1.5KW*2 and also works at an air pressure of 0.6-0.8 MPa. The maximum cutting diameter of the equipment is 35 mm and the maximum cutting depth is 60 mm. The overall dimensions of the equipment are 2000 x 2500 x 1600 mm.
long_description:
Line drilling machine US-MZ73212.

Technical parameters of the equipment:

  • Model: US-MZ73212.
  • Max drill dia: 35 mm.
  • Max drill depth: 60 mm.
  • Number of spindles: 21 x 2.
  • Spindle speed: 2840 r / min.
  • Power: 1.5*2 Kw.
  • Air pressure: 0.6 - 0.8 mpa.
  • Dimension: 2000 x 2500 x 1600 mm.
